{"tid":2346144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<12人送中> 中國律師：刑期判得太重","createTime":"2020-12-30T05:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T06:54:18.000Z","uid":227801,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f2c5dd62c5fca7f5ea6f6eca56efb39a1b3e417","tid":2346144,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"兒登仔： 輕判<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567815-20201230.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567815-20201230.htm&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=ef29ac31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567815-20201230.htm&h=e51f7134\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567815-20201230.htm</a><br />\n有關律師回應今次判決時表示，如果只在結夥偷渡中購買或駕駛船隻，絕不構成組織偷越邊境罪，即使構成犯罪，兩人作為從犯，刑期亦判得太重，法院在判決時亦沒有宣告有緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n法院在公告中表示，鄧棨然、喬映瑜是受他人組織實施犯罪，在共同犯罪中是從犯，可依法減輕處罰。<br />\n<br />\n公告又提及，今年8月，鄧棨然、喬映瑜根據他人安排，策劃組織多人由香港偷渡至台灣，由鄧棨然購買偷渡船隻，兩人在8月23日聯絡其餘10人，在香港西貢布袋澳碼頭會合，乘坐鄧棨然駕駛的船隻，船隻在廣東省管轄海域，被深圳海警局查獲，12人被依法拘留。"},{"pid":"813054e206aa30a981cdf10abc55d9e88e32eb12","tid":2346144,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"28號偷渡嚟香港嗰對支那夫婦<br />\n咁又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449b52a7d078be43ef2863294878afebe5953062","tid":2346144,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356cdfba0950941ba7317a7a08991999931f5e89","tid":2346144,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:25:45.000Z","msg":"睇返d中國走私客都係判幾個月<br />\n講緊人地係帶埋幾百萬既貨"},{"pid":"5e0c59b1bd72388f8e7d319ceac66cbda2109d0b","tid":2346144,"uid":227801,"like":0,"di